软件包 syntaxtree

接口摘要
Node The interface which all syntax tree classes must implement.
NodeListInterface The interface which NodeList, NodeListOptional, and NodeSequence implement.
 

类摘要
AllocationExpression Grammar production: f0 -> "new" f1 -> Identifier() f2 -> "(" f3 -> ")"
AndExpression Grammar production: f0 -> PrimaryExpression() f1 -> "&&" f2 -> PrimaryExpression()
ArrayAllocationExpression Grammar production: f0 -> "new" f1 -> "int" f2 -> "[" f3 -> Expression() f4 -> "]"
ArrayAssignmentStatement Grammar production: f0 -> Identifier() f1 -> "[" f2 -> Expression() f3 -> "]" f4 -> "=" f5 -> Expression() f6 -> ";"
ArrayLength Grammar production: f0 -> PrimaryExpression() f1 -> "."
ArrayLookup Grammar production: f0 -> PrimaryExpression() f1 -> "[" f2 -> PrimaryExpression() f3 -> "]"
ArrayType Grammar production: f0 -> "int" f1 -> "[" f2 -> "]"
AssignmentStatement Grammar production: f0 -> Identifier() f1 -> "=" f2 -> Expression() f3 -> ";"
Block Grammar production: f0 -> "{" f1 -> ( Statement() )* f2 -> "}"
BooleanType Grammar production: f0 -> "boolean"
BracketExpression Grammar production: f0 -> "(" f1 -> Expression() f2 -> ")"
ClassDeclaration Grammar production: f0 -> "class" f1 -> Identifier() f2 -> "{" f3 -> ( VarDeclaration() )* f4 -> ( MethodDeclaration() )* f5 -> "}"
ClassExtendsDeclaration Grammar production: f0 -> "class" f1 -> Identifier() f2 -> "extends" f3 -> Identifier() f4 -> "{" f5 -> ( VarDeclaration() )* f6 -> ( MethodDeclaration() )* f7 -> "}"
CompareExpression Grammar production: f0 -> PrimaryExpression() f1 -> "<" f2 -> PrimaryExpression()
Expression Grammar production: f0 -> AndExpression() | CompareExpression() | PlusExpression() | MinusExpression() | TimesExpression() | ArrayLookup() | ArrayLength() | MessageSend() | PrimaryExpression()
ExpressionList Grammar production: f0 -> Expression() f1 -> ( ExpressionRest() )*
ExpressionRest Grammar production: f0 -> "," f1 -> Expression()
FalseLiteral Grammar production: f0 -> "false"
FormalParameter Grammar production: f0 -> Type() f1 -> Identifier()
FormalParameterList Grammar production: f0 -> FormalParameter() f1 -> ( FormalParameterRest() )*
FormalParameterRest Grammar production: f0 -> "," f1 -> FormalParameter()
Goal Grammar production: f0 -> MainClass() f1 -> ( TypeDeclaration() )* f2 ->
Identifier Grammar production: f0 ->
IfStatement Grammar production: f0 -> "if" f1 -> "(" f2 -> Expression() f3 -> ")" f4 -> Statement() f5 -> "else" f6 -> Statement()
IntegerLiteral Grammar production: f0 ->
IntegerType Grammar production: f0 -> "int"
MainClass Grammar production: f0 -> "class" f1 -> Identifier() f2 -> "{" f3 -> "public" f4 -> "static" f5 -> "void" f6 -> "main" f7 -> "(" f8 -> "String" f9 -> "[" f10 -> "]" f11 -> Identifier() f12 -> ")" f13 -> "{" f14 -> PrintStatement() f15 -> "}" f16 -> "}"
MessageSend Grammar production: f0 -> PrimaryExpression() f1 -> "."
MethodDeclaration Grammar production: f0 -> "public" f1 -> Type() f2 -> Identifier() f3 -> "(" f4 -> ( FormalParameterList() )?
MinusExpression Grammar production: f0 -> PrimaryExpression() f1 -> "-" f2 -> PrimaryExpression()
NodeChoice Represents a grammar choice, e.g. ( A | B )
NodeList Represents a grammar list, e.g. ( A )+
NodeListOptional Represents an optional grammar list, e.g. ( A )*
NodeOptional Represents an grammar optional node, e.g. ( A )?
NodeSequence Represents a sequence of nodes nested within a choice, list, optional list, or optional, e.g. ( A B )+ or [ C D E ]
NodeToken Represents a single token in the grammar.
NotExpression Grammar production: f0 -> "!"
PlusExpression Grammar production: f0 -> PrimaryExpression() f1 -> "+" f2 -> PrimaryExpression()
PrimaryExpression Grammar production: f0 -> IntegerLiteral() | TrueLiteral() | FalseLiteral() | Identifier() | ThisExpression() | ArrayAllocationExpression() | AllocationExpression() | NotExpression() | BracketExpression()
PrintStatement Grammar production: f0 -> "System.out.println" f1 -> "(" f2 -> Expression() f3 -> ")" f4 -> ";"
Statement Grammar production: f0 -> Block() | AssignmentStatement() | ArrayAssignmentStatement() | IfStatement() | WhileStatement() | PrintStatement()
ThisExpression Grammar production: f0 -> "this"
TimesExpression Grammar production: f0 -> PrimaryExpression() f1 -> "*" f2 -> PrimaryExpression()
TrueLiteral Grammar production: f0 -> "true"
Type Grammar production: f0 -> ArrayType() | BooleanType() | IntegerType() | Identifier()
TypeDeclaration Grammar production: f0 -> ClassDeclaration() | ClassExtendsDeclaration()
VarDeclaration Grammar production: f0 -> Type() f1 -> Identifier() f2 -> ";"
WhileStatement Grammar production: f0 -> "while" f1 -> "(" f2 -> Expression() f3 -> ")" f4 -> Statement()
